      <title>伊朗总统佩泽什基安在以色列紧张局势升温之际任命内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/iran-s-pezeshkian-names-cabinet-amid-simmering-israel-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗改革派总统马苏德·佩泽什基安选择了 2015 年核协议的设计者之一担任外交部长，并选择了一位业内资深人士担任石油行业最高职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/iran-s-pezeshkian-names-cabinet-amid-simmering-israel-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 11:13:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗导弹部队在伊拉克边境附近进行军事演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/iran-missile-unit-conducting-military-drills-near-iraqi-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据伊朗伊斯兰共和国通讯社报道，伊朗军队的一个导弹部队正在伊拉克边境附近进行演习，以“提高该地区军队的作战准备程度”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/iran-missile-unit-conducting-military-drills-near-iraqi-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 10:33:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯反击入侵乌克兰，导弹在基辅附近造成两人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/war-in-ukraine-russia-hits-back-in-kursk-missile-kills-two-near-kyiv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基敦促盟友允许乌克兰深入俄罗斯领土，他的军队继续守住上周突然跨境入侵所取得的胜利，一次导弹袭击造成基辅附近的两人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/war-in-ukraine-russia-hits-back-in-kursk-missile-kills-two-near-kyiv</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 09:10:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗新总统任命石油部长为内阁成员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/iran-s-new-president-names-oil-minister-in-cabinet-rollout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据伊朗半官方的伊朗学生通讯社报道，伊朗国营国家石油公司前副手穆赫辛·帕克内贾德被任命为伊朗新任石油部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/iran-s-new-president-names-oil-minister-in-cabinet-rollout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 09:05:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾总统马科斯批评中国在领空采取“鲁莽”行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/philippines-marcos-blasts-china-for-reckless-move-in-airspace</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯表示，中国空军对在南海浅滩巡逻的菲律宾飞机采取的行动是“无理、非法和鲁莽的”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/philippines-marcos-blasts-china-for-reckless-move-in-airspace</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 07:35:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗承诺以“合法、坚决”的方式惩罚以色列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/iran-promises-to-punish-israel-in-legitimate-resolute-manner</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗代理外交部长重申，伊朗决心惩罚以色列上个月在德黑兰杀害哈马斯高级领导人的行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/iran-promises-to-punish-israel-in-legitimate-resolute-manner</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 05:35:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>决定孟加拉国未来的关键人物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/the-key-people-who-will-shape-bangladesh-s-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国经历了一周的动荡之后，临时政府现已成立，开始着手为这个南亚国家带来稳定和秩序的艰巨工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/the-key-people-who-will-shape-bangladesh-s-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 03:55:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯支持取消小费税，采纳特朗普喜欢的想法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/harris-backs-ending-taxes-on-tips-adopting-idea-trump-floated</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯表示，她将寻求取消服务行业工人的小费收入税——这与她的 2024 年竞争对手共和党人唐纳德·特朗普提出的一项提议相一致，旨在争取年轻人和工薪阶层选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/harris-backs-ending-taxes-on-tips-adopting-idea-trump-floated</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 02:50:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称微软曾告诉他的竞选团队，伊朗是黑客攻击的幕后黑手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/trump-campaign-says-it-was-hacked-suggests-iran-to-blame</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普表示，微软公司告知他，他的一个竞选网站遭到伊朗政府攻击，但他说黑客在此次攻击中只能访问“公开信息”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/trump-campaign-says-it-was-hacked-suggests-iran-to-blame</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 19:51:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称袭击了加沙学校内的哈马斯指挥部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/israel-strike-on-gaza-school-kills-100-palestinians-hamas-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方称，以色列对加沙市发动的致命袭击遭到国际社会谴责，袭击目标是设在一所学校和相邻清真寺内的哈马斯“指挥和控制中心”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/israel-strike-on-gaza-school-kills-100-palestinians-hamas-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 04:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
